'''Katemera wa Hepataitisi B''' ndi [[vaccine|katemera]] amene amathandiza kupewa matenda a [[hepatitis B|hepataitisi B]].<ref name="WHO20092">{{cite journal|title=Hepatitis B vaccines WHO position paper|journal=Weekly epidemiological record|date=2 Oct 2009|volume=40|issue=84|page=405-420|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2009/wer8440.pdf}}</ref> Mwana aliyense akangobadwa amayenera kupatsidwa katemerayu pasanapite maola 24 mwanayo atabadwa, ndipo kenako angalandire katemera wachiwiri ndiponso wachitatu pakapita nthawi.<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Ngakhale ana omwe ali ndi [[Immunosuppression|chitetezo chochepa m'thupi]] mwina chifukwa cha [[HIV/AIDS]] kapena omwe [[Premature infant|anabadwa masiku asanakwane]]  ayenera kulandira katemerayu.<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Kwa anthu omwe alibe mavuto  ena m'thupi, katemerayu amathandiza kwambiri moti anthu 95 pa 100 aliwonse amene alandira katemerayu sangadwale.<ref name="WHO20092" /><!-- Administration -->

Anthu omwe ali m'madera amene matendawa ndi ofala kwambiri amayenera kuyezetsa magazi kuti atsimikizire ngati katemerayu akugwira bwino ntchito.<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Ndipo anthu a m'mayiko amene matendawa ndi ofala kwambiri amayenera kulandira katemera wowonjezera pakapita nthawi, chomodzimodzinso ndi anthu omwe chitetezo chawo n'chochepa m'thupi.<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Anthu omwe sanalandire katemerayu koma apezeka m'dera limene  [[hepatitis B virus|mavailasi a hepataitisi B]] ndi ofala kwambiri akuyenera kulandira katemera wa [[hepatitis B immune globulin|hepataitisi B immune globulin]].<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Katemerayu amaperekedwa kudzera [[Intramuscular|m'jakisoni]].<ref name="WHO20092" /><!-- Safety and formulation -->

Katemera wa hepataitisi B sabweretsa mavuto aliwonse odetsa nkhawa.<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Mavuto ochepa amene angakhalepo angakhale kumva ululu pamene munthu wabayidwa jakisoni wa katemerayu.<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Katemerayu alibe mavuto aliwonse ngati munthu atamulandira pa nthawi imene ali [[pregnancy|woyembekezera]] ngakhalenso pa nthawi imene [[breastfeeding|akuyamwitsa]].<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Ndiponso palibe umboni wosonyeza kuti katemerayu angayambitse mavuto ena monga matenda otchedwa [[Guillain-Barre syndrome|Guillain-Barre]] .<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Katemera wa matendawa amapangidwa ndi njira zamakono pogwiritsa ntchito tizigawo tina [[recombinant DNA|ta DNA]].<!-- <ref name=WHO2009/> --> Katemerayu amathanso kuphatikizidwa ndi mankhwala ena a katemera wa mitundu ina.<ref name="WHO20092" />

<!-- HIstory, society and culture -->
Katemera wa hepataitisi B anavomerezedwa koyamba m'dziko la United States m'chaka cha 1981.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Moticka|first1=Edward|title=A Historical Perspective on Evidence-Based Immunology|isbn=9780123983756|page=336|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=2TMwAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA336}}</ref> Kenako mu 1986 panapangidwa mtundu wina wa katemera womwe ndi wabwino poyerekezera ndi woyamba uja.<ref name="WHO20092" /> Katemerayu ali pagulu la [[World Health Organization's List of Essential Medicines]], yemwe ndi katemera wofunika kwambiri pa moyo wa munthu amene ayenera kuperedwa ndi [[health system|a zaumoyo komanso a zachipatala]].<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013}}</ref> M'chaka cha 2014, mtengo wogulitsira katemerayu pachipiku unali woyambira pa madola a ku America 0.58 mpaka 13.20 pa katemera m'modzi.<ref>{{cite web|title=Vaccine, Hepatitis B|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=HEPBV&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=&desc=Vaccine%2C%20Hepatitis%20B&pack=new&frm=VIAL&rte=INJ&class_code2=19%2E3%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2819%2E3%2E%29Vaccines%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=6 December 2015}}</ref> Koma ku United States, mtengo wa katemerayu umayambira pa madola 50 mpaka 100.<ref name="Ric2015">{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=314}}</ref>

